---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Safety Resources" description="Bicycle safety tips and resources for Los Angeles cyclists.">
  <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-6">
    Stay safe while cycling in Los Angeles with these resources and tips.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Safety Tips</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-muted space-y-2 mb-6">
    <li>Always wear a helmet</li>
    <li>Use front and rear lights when riding at night</li>
    <li>Follow traffic laws — ride with traffic, obey signals</li>
    <li>Use bike lanes and protected infrastructure when available</li>
    <li>Make yourself visible with bright or reflective clothing</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Report Infrastructure Issues</h2>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    Report potholes, damaged bike lanes, or other infrastructure issues through the LA 311 system.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Report Bike Theft</h2>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    File a report with LAPD and register your bicycle serial number to increase recovery chances.
  </p>
</PageLayout>
